(1, 36, 25, 25, 'kjv', 'Dishon, and Aholibamah', 37, 59, 'greek', 'Name Meaning Insight', 'Dishon (H1786) - a name meaning ''to be strong'' or ''fierce'', which may imply strength in character. Aholibamah (H173), meaning ''tent of the high place'', reflects her significance as a notable figure in Edomite society.', 'textformat.abc', '[{"type": "strongs", "reference": "H1786", "description": "Strong''s number for the meaning of Dishon."}, {"type": "strongs", "reference": "H173", "description": "Strong''s number for the meaning of Aholibamah."}]'::jsonb, 'standard', false, 'v1.0', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
